data.description: THIS IS A BEAUTIFUL THREE BEDROOM, 2 FULL BATHROOM HOME! THROUGH THE HOME YOU HAVE NEWLY INSTALLED WINDOWS WITH NEW CEILFANS AND LIGHT FIXTURES. LIVING ROOM IS SPACIOUS WITH A NICE AND SLEEK FIREPLACE. KITCHEN HAS GRANITE COUNTERTOPS AND CABINETRY. FOR MORE PANTRY SPACE A NEWLY CABINETRYWAS INSTALLED BESIDE THE STOVE. KITCHEN HAS LAMIATE FLOORS THAT RUNS THROUGHOUT THE DINING AREA AND OTHER PARTS OF THE HOME. A STAINLESS STEEL DISHWASHER AND STOVE COMES WITH THE HOME.  GORGEOUS NEW BAY WINDOW IN DINING AREA. GUEST BATHROOM HAS BRAND NEW DOUBLE MIRRORS AND BACKSPLASH OVER THE TUB WITH A DUAL FLUSH TOLIET.  1ST AND 2ND BEDROOM ARE A NICE SIZE. 2ND BEDROOM IS TILED. MASTER BEDROOM IS BIG IN SIZE WITH A WALK IN CLOSET, BUILT IN SHELF AND NIGHT STANDS. MASTER BATHROOM HAS A DUAL FLUSH TOILET AND EN SUITE SOAKER TUB.  WARRANTIES LIKE NO OTHERS- ROOF, FOUNDATION, A/C, WINDOW! COME CHECK OUT YOUR NEXT HOME!
